name: SOVEREIGNTY
description:
(6/5) Social Norms and Misjudgments - Chase

Through her history of living up to social norms and carrying out the stereotypes given to her, she had finally said enough. It was time to break free of the cage that was encapsulating her, and she did. She sailed away from the burdens that stared at her spine, facing the freedom of the horizon. 

Model: Luisa I. Short  

This mint is created to help spread awareness and make meaningful impacts on those who need it within the community. This is a conceptual series related to the stereotypes and social norms we see in our daily lives.
